sometimes all you need is a little pause 🌿
for my birthday this year, i gifted myself a short escape to karjat  and oh, what a dream. from breakfast in the pool to walking barefoot around the gorgeous property, everything about this place felt like a hug to my tired soul.
the room, the calm, the skies, the stillness just what my bombay brain needed to reset.
highly recommend if you’re looking for a peaceful break that feels like magic (but just a drive away 🤍)

The only kind of plans I’m saying yes to this May? The ones that look exactly like this 🤍☀️

Took a little time off around my birthday, and honestly… these two days were the best of the year so far. Pool dips, breakfast in the water, indoor games, coffee with a view, sunsets that made me feel, and food that made me dance! 💌
Just me, celebrating me—slow mornings, soft moments, and zero guilt about doing nothing but enjoying everything.🫶💗🥰
